headline: Lisbon's Gloria funicular derails, plunging the city into mourning
description: While awaiting the results of the investigation, the mayor of the Portuguese capital has ordered the immediate suspension of all other funiculars in the city for technical inspections. The French Ministry of Foreign Affairs announced that a French national was among the injured.

headline: French women's boxing team barred from world championships after late gender tests
description: The team had traveled to the United Kingdom to undergo genetic sex tests that are banned in France but newly mandatory under the championships' regulations. Assured the tests would arrive on time, the French team slammed World Boxing's decision to reject them after the deadline passed.
